OL,3,CCharity heads to Somalia to help
OL,4,Cdisplaced families
OL,6,FThe Cornish charity is warning that
OL,7,Faround a million people left displaced
OL,8,Fin Somalia urgently need shelter.
OL,10,FThe international disaster relief
OL,11,Fcharity has launched a fundraising
OL,12,Fappeal to raise #150,000 to build
OL,13,Frobust shelters that can better
OL,14,Fwithstand weather extremes.
OL,16,FThe charity says it's using a
OL,17,Fdifferent type of shelter in Somalia
OL,18,Fas it is expected people will remain
OL,19,Fdisplaced for longer without proper
OL,20,Fsupport to build homes.
