OL,3,CCharity heads to Somalia to help
OL,4,Cdisplaced families
OL,6,FShelterBox says that with the changing
OL,7,Fclimate and growing displacement, it's
OL,8,Fhaving to change the way it works by
OL,9,Fdeveloping different types of shelters.
OL,11,FSpeaking from Mogadishu, ShelterBox's
OL,12,Fprogramme manager Mel Hughes said: "We
OL,13,Fare launching a campaign for #150,000
OL,14,Fthat will go to communities like the
OL,15,Fones we are seeing in Somalia where
OL,16,Ffloods are devastating communities.
