OL,3,CCharity heads to Somalia to help
OL,4,Cdisplaced families
OL,6,F"In Somalia we know that the rainy
OL,7,Fseason is coming again and people have
OL,8,Fbarely had a chance to recover from
OL,9,Fthe last season. Communities tell us
OL,10,Fthat without a shelter they have
OL,11,Flittle hope."
OL,13,FAmong those supported so far by
OL,14,FShelterBox is 30-year-old mother
OL,15,FNurta. She and her family were forced
OL,16,Fto leave their relatively comfortable
OL,17,Flife and abandon the land they owned
OL,18,Fand farmed after prolonged periods of
OL,19,Fdrought left them without water.
