OL,3,CCharity heads to Somalia to help
OL,4,Cdisplaced families
OL,6,FThe family are now living in one of
OL,7,Fthe shelters ShelterBox has helped
OL,8,Fprovide on the outskirts of Baidoa.
OL,10,FShe said: "I find myself living away
OL,11,Ffrom my homeland for the past two
OL,12,Fyears. Our journey to this point was
OL,13,Fmarked by a series of hardships
OL,14,Fprimarily driven by the recurring and
OL,15,Fdevastating droughts that plagued our
OL,16,Fregion."JShelterbox says that Somalia
OL,17,Fhas not brought on the problems of
OL,18,Fclimate change, but it is suffering
OL,19,Fthe consequences and urgently needs
OL,20,Fhelp.
