OL,3,CCharity heads to Somalia to help
OL,4,Cdisplaced families
OL,6,FMel said: "The conditions of flood,
OL,7,Fdrought and conflict are being made
OL,8,Fworse by climate change. Somalia only
OL,9,Fcontributes 0.03 per cent of the
OL,10,Fworld's carbon and yet you can see the
OL,11,Fdevastating impact it's having.
OL,13,F"This is a really clear example that,
OL,14,Fclimate change is making things so
OL,15,Fmuch worse for people in Somalia."
